description: Hi Everyone! I'm inviting you to an upcoming potluck I'm co-hosting on August 17 called, #BayAreaVeganPotluck. If you happen to be in the area, please feel free to join us for some (vegan) food, fun, and giveaways. Yes, the hosts will be giving away prizes. I hope to see you then! Just RSVP to bayareaveganpotluck@gmail.com with the dish that you'll be bringing. See ya!
